      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Product Photo Studio (n8n Form)\n**Model:** KIE.AI nano-banana-2 (image to image)\n\n### Setup\n1. Add an **HTTP Bearer Auth** credential with your KIE.AI API key and select it on the 3 KIE.AI HTTP nodes (Upload Input to KIE, Create Task, Poll Task Status).\n2. Add an **OpenAI** credential and select it on the OpenAI Chat Model node.\n3. Activate the workflow and open the form URL from the trigger.\n\n### How it works\nForm submission -> upload photo to KIE.AI -> AI enhances the prompt -> nano-banana-2 generates the image -> poll until done -> show the result on the form.",
